Also you will surely be impressed by the low maintenance front yards with water feature, Buddha painting and has the double car garage.
The premium inclusions do not stop there;
Ducted heating & Cooling

Address: Lot 15 Bella Rosa Estate Werribee VIC 3030
Description:
Lot 15 Bella Rosa Estate, Werribee
Ray White Truganina Proudly presents this great opportunity to build your dream home, on this beautiful block of land in the highly sought after Bella Rosa Estate in Werribee.
Stage 3 Now Selling
Imagine establishing a new life for you and your family in an established community that is bordered by established streets and all the amenities that come with it. This can all be yours at Bella Rosa Werribee.
Centrally located close to all things convenient, Bella Rosa offers precious exclusivity that can only come from being a brand new community neighbouring the admired St. Andrew's Estate, an established residential locality. The perfect mix of location and land upon which to create the ultimate lifestyle has been selected - all you need to do is hand pick the position that suits you.
Only 30 minute drive to the Melbourne CBD, Bella Rosa is a unique residential opportunity with leafy surrounds, striking streetscapes and an exciting array of extraordinary living choices. Residents will enjoy easy train, bus and road access to all major Melbourne destinations, and when travelling by air, will have the choice of Melbourne and Avalon Airports located within 30 minute drive from the estate.
Closer to home it is a short drive to local shopping centres such as Werribee Plaza where you can satisfy all your shopping requirements. A range of primary and secondary schools and higher education facilities are also close by, including the highly sought after St. Andrews Primary School and the Victoria University Werribee Campus.
Vast open spaces are close at hand including Gordon O'Keife Reserve and the Werribee Racecourse. Werribee Park, home to Werribee Park Mansion, Victoria's Open Range Zoo, the State Rose Garden and the State Equestrian Centre and Hotel is another must see attraction that is right at your doorstep.
For those who love the water, Werribee South beach is just minutes away and is perfect for swimming, fishing, boating, and strolling - or for just building sandcastles with the kids. Life gets even easier with a range of excellent schools, shops, eateries, transport and recreational facilities all at your doorstep, meaning you will be well positioned to enjoy the best that Werribee has to offer.
Saturday mornings can be spent playing a game of golf at the Werribee Park Golf Club, or enjoying getting back to nature at Werribee Park which contains Werribee Park Mansion, Victoria's Open Range Zoo and the State Rose Garden. The possibilities are truly limitless.
Please call Yash on 0410 840 500 or Mark on 0425 400 600 to find out more!

Description:
Limitless Opportunity in Saltwater Coast Estate
LJ Hooker Point Cook presents 68 Sunman Drive, Point Cook. Nestled within the sought-after Saltwater Coast Estate, this vacant parcel of land is the opportunity to secure the future of your dreams. A coastal community with an emphasis on lifestyle, this splendid location is the sea-change you have been longing for. Imagine picnics in the park and long walks along winding ocean paths, retreating at days end to your newly built home.
With a south/southwest orientation, this regular shaped 526 square meter allotment boasts a 13.26-meter frontage and a 34.85-meter depth, accommodating both single and double-storey dwellings with ease. With space for a sizeable back yard, vegetable gardens, an enviable entertainers deck or even an inground pool, the only limit here is your imagination.
Well-established and with easy access to every amenity, Saltwater Coast Estate offers an array of leisure activities, including the spectacular Lifestyle Centre, with a fully equipped gym, indoor and outdoor swimming pools, tennis courts, function rooms, barbeque areas and a cafe. Nearby, the Saltwater Coast Wetlands, Reverse, Crocodile Park and Community Centre offer fun and entertainment for all ages.
For families, a choice of quality educational facilities includes Saltwater P-9 College, St Mary of the Cross Catholic Primary School, Alamanda K-9 College, Lumen Christi School and Carranballac College (Jamieson Way Campus). For little ones, childcare options include Creative Garden Early Learning and Kids Resort Early Learning Centre.
For ease of living, a variety of shopping precincts are just moments away, including Sanctuary Lakes Shopping Centre, Point Cook Town Centre and Featherbrook Shopping Centre. Commuters will enjoy an easy journey to Melbournes CBD, with public transport options including well-serviced bus routes and the nearby Williams Landing Station.

Description:
Alluring Allcrest
For the opportunity to view this home in real time via virtual inspection, request an inspection or contact your LJ Hooker agent to organise a time. During the virtual inspection, you will be able to do a virtual walk through of the home and ask your agent any questions about the home. Please note real time virtual inspections will be held in accordance with the current Covid-19 directions and will be performed with the assistance of homeowners.
LJ Hooker Point Cook presents 10 Allcrest Way, Truganina. Alluring and attractive, this immaculately presented four-and-a-half-year-old property makes the perfect first home or ideal investment. Comprising two living zones, three bedrooms, two bathrooms and double car accommodation, this residence is light and bright, faultlessly created by Simonds Builders. Nestled within the tranquil Bellevue Estate and within easy reach of all amenities, residents will enjoy proximity to quality schools, local shops and public transport.
- With sensational street appeal, this classic yet contemporary home is warm and welcoming, beginning with a chic and stylish entry way with floating timber flooring which weaves throughout the home. The adjacent formal lounge / theatre room is a versatile inclusion, a flexible space which caters to families, easily transformed into a childrens playroom or home office.
- Signifying divine design, the open plan family and meals zone is generous in size, encompassing the kitchen and extending the to enclosed alfresco. Entertainers will enjoy the seamless integration of indoors and out, providing plenty of space to host family and friends.
- Central to the home, the glossy kitchen awaits culinary creations, with clean lines and stone countertops, a breakfast bar and pendant lighting. Quality stainless-steel appliances include an enviable 900mm gas cooktop and 900mm under bench oven, a canopy rangehood and dishwasher, while a walk-in pantry provides ample storage.
- Three spacious bedrooms are offered, including the delightful master suite, located at the front of the home and complete with a walk-in-robe and en suite. The remaining bedrooms are fitted with built-in robes and soft carpets underfoot, sharing access to the family bathroom with a tub and separate toilet.
- This single-storey residence enjoys a flat and fully fenced block, with low maintenance landscaping, artificial turf and a well-established vegetable garden.
- Further highlights of this wonderful home include a double remote-control garage with internal access, an internal laundry, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, 12 solar panels, luxe timber shutters, security screens and downlights throughout.
Truganina is a vibrant family-oriented community, surrounded by quality schools including Truganina P-9 College, St Clares Catholic Primary School, Westbourne Grammar and Thomas Carr College. Local amenities include Wyndham Village Shopping Centre, Tarneit Central Shopping Centre and Healthwest Medical Centre, as well as a variety of specialty retailers and dining options. Recreational facilities include the walking paths and green spaces of Skeleton Waterholes Creek, while commuters will benefit from the close proximity to Tarneit Train Station.

Description:
Lifestyle Location
With vacant land becoming so rare this close to the city, the perfect opportunity has arisen to secure one of last remaining vacant parcels of land in the estate. Please note the grant for building a new dwelling along with the added bonus of no stamp duty on the purchase applies to first home buyers. 8 Maxwelton Circuit Derrimut offers the ultimate location, a peaceful and quiet cul de sac with no through traffic yet with everything from Deer Park train station, bus services, shopping facilities, schools, sporting facilities, kids play centres, parkland, cafes and restaurants all within a leisurely walk. In addition Derrimut offers easy access to freeways, close proximity to city and a history of tremendous capital growth making the purchase of this land not just a lifestyle opportunity but a shrewd investment as well.

Description:
SOLD BY RAJ PANJWANI .. Please Call On 0470 648 329
This meticulously built house will sway you at the outset, with its elegant design, its aesthetic appeal and its sheer virtuosity in space usage. Designed and constructed by PORTER DAVIS, it is situated in a quiet and harmonious location of Truganina.
Only on the rarest occasion does an allotment offering such dramatic dimensions and irresistible potential become available in such a rewarding context as this sought after quiet court location, here in the heart of Truganina. Boasting a sundrenched frontage and sleek contemporary spaces, this immaculate & sensationally stylish home offers an exceptional lifestyle which is just waiting to be enjoyed.
With close proximity to the popular schools such as Truganina South Primary, Westbourne Grammar School, Al-Taqwa College, Wyndham Village Shopping Centre, Williams Landing & Tarneit Train Stations, Parks, Walking Tracks, Local Community Centre, Shops & Easy Freeway Access, convenience and comfort can't get any better than this!
Exquisitely maintained , it's been a home to a caring owner-occupier family, thereby providing an excellent opportunity for the new owner to move in instantly or to reap the benefits of a rewarding investment.
The designer kitchen is a chef's reverie with stunning stone top benches, 900 MM stainless steel gas cooker, range hood and a spacious pantry. An icing on the cake is the huge island that is perfect for casual meals.
Overall the residence is equipped with quality fixtures and fittings throughout and is beautifully presented that is guaranteed to impress the owners and visitors alike!
# Master with Ensuite & WIR
# Bedrooms w/ BIR'S
# Remote Controlled Double Garage
# Low Maintenance Side Yard
# Ducted Heating
# Backyard with Timber Decking and Pergola
# Floor coverings - Carpet/Floor tiles
This opportunity that gives you the dream home you always want is not to be missed! Call Raj on 0470 648 329 or Sachin on 0433 110 100 to arrange an inspection as this won't last long.
